# Project Core

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for architecture, gotchas, and skill index.

## Essentials

- Imports: `@/` alias maps to `src/` — never deep relative paths across modules
- Dev server: port **3002** (`npm run dev`)
- Business logic in `src/lib/`; UI in `src/components/`; routes in `src/app/`
- Canonical prod URL: `https://pokemon-indol-tau.vercel.app` — not `pokemon.ultharcr.com`

## File placement

| Type | Location |
|------|----------|
| Pages / API routes | `src/app/` |
| Reusable components | `src/components/` |
| Hooks | `src/hooks/` |
| Services / engine | `src/lib/` |
| Shared types | `src/types/` |
| Tests | `__tests__/` subdirs co-located with source |

## Before finishing

- Run relevant tests from AGENTS.md testing matrix
- Minimize diff scope — match existing patterns in surrounding files
- Do not commit secrets or `.env` files
